      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor category.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty (turbulence model selection, hemolysis power-law model constants) not formally assessed at MRL 2. SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on literature consensus for rotating machinery flows."
    },
