    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou1-decision",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels at Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Mesh convergence GCI of 1.8% and output comparison deviations below 15% across all operating points provide sufficient confidence in CFD hemolysis predictions for the stated COU. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
